#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Inledning"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The TNEF File Viewer allows to handle easily mail attachments using the TNEF "
"format. Those attachments are usually found in mails coming from <trademark "
"class=\"registered\">Microsoft</trademark> mail servers and embed the mail "
"properties as well as the actual attachments."
msgstr ""
"TNEF-filvisaren gör det möjligt att enkelt hantera e-postbilagor som "
"använder TNEF-formatet. Dessa bilagor hittas oftast i brev som kommer från "
"<trademark class=\"registered\">Microsoft</trademark> e-postservrar och "
"inbäddar brevegenskaperna samt själva bilagorna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An attachment in TNEF format is most often named <filename>winmail.dat</"
"filename> or <filename>win.dat</filename>."
msgstr ""
"En bilaga med TNEF-format heter oftast <filename>winmail.dat</filename> "
"eller <filename>win.dat</filename>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>TNEF Main Window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Huvudfönstret i TNEF</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>TNEF Main Window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Huvudfönstret i TNEF</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This utility program allows to perform various operations on those "
"attachments:"
msgstr ""
"Det här verktyget tillåter att diverse åtgärder utförs med dessa bilagor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "View/open attachments with associated applications."
msgstr "Visa eller öppna bilagor med tillhörande program."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extract actual attachments"
msgstr "Extrahera själva bilagorna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "View message properties (TNEF/MAPI)"
msgstr "Visa brevegenskaper (TNEF/MAPI)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "View/extract message formatted text (in RTF format)"
msgstr "Visa och extrahera brevets formaterade text (med RTF-format)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; automatically shows the content of a TNEF attachment. You can open "
"or save the attachments using the actions in the context menu."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; visar automatiskt innehållet i en TNEF-bilaga. Det går att öppna "
"eller spara bilagan med alternativen i den sammanhangsberoende menyn."

#. Tag: screeninfo
